scene.message:
Yukino: {ctl0f:1}!{nl}
This person is still alive!{nl}
Help me!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: {ctl0f:1}!{nl}
That nurse is beyond saving!{nl}
If we drag our feet,{nl}
we'll meet the same fate!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Hey, {ctl0f:1}!{nl}
The monsters are right{nl}
on top of us!{waitkey}{ret}

Nurse: I... I'm done for...{nl}
You kids... just get{nl}
out of here...{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Oh my, good day!{nl}
My goodness!{nl}
There are Demons here too?{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Are you serious!?{nl}
This person is still alive!{nl}
You're saying abandon her!?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Honestly...{nl}
Don't come crying to me when{nl}
you end up like them.{waitkey}{ret}
